    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "The area’s history has been shaped by its closeness to the Gulf of Mexico and its rich estuarine environment.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        4
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://www.wisdomlib.org/cities/upper-grand-lagoon-27293"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "The Grand Lagoon Coalition aims to turn the unincorporated east end of Panama City Beach into a vibrant community that celebrates its history and personality.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        3
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 1"
      ],
      "source": "https://grandlagoon.com/about/"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "For years, the Grand Lagoon has been the fastest and easiest way for tourists and locals to reach the Gulf.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        22
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 1"
      ],
      "source": "https://grandlagoon.com/about/"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Fishing—both deep‑sea and inshore—has become a hub here, alongside fine dining and family activities.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
